    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The king has issued a call to arms, inviting any adventurers bold enough to step forward. Only the worthy will be selected for his secret quest: to join his covenant in search of the legendary Crystal of Light!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an adventure across a fantasy world with a party of 8 playable characters, each with their own weapons and unique abilities! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of towns and dungeons to explore, with multiple different environments and methods of travel! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Target enemy weaknesses to stun and lower their defenses, and power up your attacks even more by using Boost Points to increase the strength or number of attacks a character uses to inflict massive damage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070320/extras/994bfdb0808d7145f783da1749fb56ea.poster.avif?t=1756008279\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070320/extras/994bfdb0808d7145f783da1749fb56ea.webm?t=1756008279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070320/extras/994bfdb0808d7145f783da1749fb56ea.mp4?t=1756008279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch equipped weapons or even inactive party members into battle during any party member's turn... mid-combat!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070320/extras/7199932ff9dc1e0566ff109b380d6547.poster.avif?t=1756008279\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070320/extras/7199932ff9dc1e0566ff109b380d6547.webm?t=1756008279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070320/extras/7199932ff9dc1e0566ff109b380d6547.mp4?t=1756008279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be ready for any encounter by spending Ability Points earned from defeating enemies to learn new abilities!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070320/extras/674f5c063343b76bab6c3eba6fd6af08.poster.avif?t=1756008279\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070320/extras/674f5c063343b76bab6c3eba6fd6af08.webm?t=1756008279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070320/extras/674f5c063343b76bab6c3eba6fd6af08.mp4?t=1756008279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto Battle can be enabled for players looking for a more casual experience. Additionally, battles with normal enemies can always be escaped from, avoiding the need to battle every enemy when you'd rather explore.</p></li></ul>",
